Data Deletion Instructions
To request the deletion of your data, follow these steps:

Submit a Request:
Visit our Data Deletion Request Form and fill in the required fields.
Make sure to include your account details and specify which data you'd like to delete.
Verification Process:
After submitting your request, we will send you a verification email.
Follow the instructions in the email to confirm your request.
Processing Your Request:
Once verified, our team will process your data deletion request within [X] business days.
You will receive an email notification once your data has been deleted successfully.
Important Notes:
Data deletion is permanent. Once deleted, it cannot be recovered.
Please be aware that some data may need to be retained due to legal or regulatory requirements.
If you have any questions or need further assistance, please contact our support team at [lnarsia12@gmail.com].
Thank you for choosing us!
